room_title: Escape room "Bamboozled Room" by Bamboozled Escape Room in Houston
review: Love this place! Been twice now! Rooms are challenging but fun. If you get stuck they help along the way but just enough. Can't wait to go back again!

room_title: Escape room "Bamboozled Room" by Bamboozled Escape Room in Houston
review: We had a lot of fun even though we got bamboozled! I would definitely recommend it to anyone who is looking to go out and try something different! Thanks for being very nice as well!
